Package framework.components

This package contains the def.electron library (source: Definitely Typed).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CardLayout
    Simple card layout component
    Contains convenient methods to stack containers over other containers and show one at a time.
    CardLayoutItem
    Simple container used as child item for the CardLayout container.
    ExternalJavascript
    Class that is rendered as javascript source tag as shown below

    <script type="text/javascript" src="??"></script>
    ExternalStylesheet
    Rendered as an external stylesheet call tag as show below

    <link rel="stylesheet" media="|all|screen|print|speech" crossorigin="|anonymous|use-credentials" type="text/css" source="??"></link>
    HTMLTemplateContainer
    A component that is rendered with a specified html template.
    Instead of having just a tag like other component, this component body is an html template.
    Children of this component are placed according to the name of the component.
    E.g.
    JSContainer
    Most basic component built in with a default Renderer
    An instance of this component will render a simple tag in the browser.
